post.description:
Send as `multipart/form-data`. `Entries` is a JSON-serialized array of working-time entries;
`FormFile` is the timesheet document (PDF, JPG/JPEG or PNG). Bookings and the user-visible
timesheet document are committed together after file storage rows are prepared.
